LEDI.Name: Animosity
LEDI.Message: Hard stares tipped with poisonous rage.

LEDI.Name: Coercion
LEDI.Message: Glowing slivers of glass, fresh from the vise and beyond credulity.

LEDI.Name: Dynamo
LEDI.Message: Oh what a monotonous cycle, yielding so little.

LEDI.Name: Errant
LEDI.Message: Travelling far and wide; short and stumpy.

LEDI.Name: Eulogy
LEDI.Message: A spoonful of sugar can do more harm than good.

LEDI.Name: Feral
LEDI.Message: Instincts abound and thought is immaterial.

LEDI.Name: Lucid
LEDI.Message: Why try to understand the world through a microscope?

LEDI.Name: Moussaka
LEDI.Message: Someone put grenades in my eggplant.

LEDI.Name: Ormolu
LEDI.Message: After all these years, the folks at Knox were very disappointed.

LEDI.Name: Watery Keep
LEDI.Message: Ancient legend has it, water was transported here via a tube.
